<TEXT>
<P>
 Marc Reisner's "Handicapped by Our Attitude," (Commentary, May 23), said it 
all, and very well; if we don't stop looking to Washington every time 
California burns up, dries up, drowns or falls apart, tomorrow's headline will 
be: "Congress to California: Drop Dead." 
</P>
<P>
