<DATE>
<P>
June 10, 1994, Friday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 12; Column 5 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
508 words 
