<P>
 "Billy Lemon and the Warning" will kick off the city's summer concerts in the 
park July 7 with 1950s, '60s and '90s music. 
</P>
<P>
 The free summer concerts, featuring a lineup of three bands during July and 
August, will be held from 6:30 to 8 p.m. at the Fountain Valley Recreation 
