 * Pierce College Extension, 6291 Winnetka Ave., Woodland Hills. Classes for 
children 4 and older start July 5. Best bets: "Magic" ($46), "Puppet-Making and 
Performing" ($56), "Bug World" ($23), "Cloudy With a Chance of Rain" (weather 
forecasting, $35), "X Marks the Spot" (map-reading, $36), "Minding Your P's and 
Q's" (manners, $35), "Children's Theater" ($33-$49), "Vaudeville" ($35), 
"Surfing" ($59). Call (818) 719-6425. 
</P>
<P>
 * Valley College Community Services, 5800 Fulton Ave., Van Nuys. Classes for 
children 6 and older start June 7. Best bets: "TV Commercial and Acting 
Workshop" (taught by one of the Doublemint chewing-gum twins, $49), "Golf" 
($34), "Horsemanship" ($146), "Kid's Club Jam" (choreography, hip-hop and funk 
dance, $37). Call (818) 988-3911. MARYANN HAMMERS 
