<P>
 Medical licenses -- A listing of medical disciplinary actions provided by the 
Medical Board of California and published in The Times on June 1 did not 
accurately reflect the status of Dr. Yuzef Gurovich's medical license. In fact, 
Dr. Gurovich successfully completed his probation and his license is clear and 
current. 
