<P>
 Court case -- A May 31 article inaccurately portrayed the district attorney's 
position in a workers' compensation fraud case. Ronald Lopez of Oxnard pleaded 
guilty to a misdemeanor after Acting Superior Court Judge Bruce A. Clark agreed 
to reduce the charge from a felony. Prosecutors objected to the agreement. 
