<P>
 Computerland outlets -- An article Thursday on Merisel Inc., a computer 
hardware and software wholesaler, incorrectly described the relationship 
between the company and 160 Computerland retail outlets. A unit of Merisel is 
the franchiser for those stores, which are independently owned. 
